Uses of Interface
picocli.CommandLine.IFactory

  • Packages that use CommandLine.IFactory 
    Package Description
    picocli
    Provides classes and interfaces for the main picocli command line parsing and autocompletion functionality.
    picocli.shell.jline3
    Provides classes and interfaces for integrating picocli with JLine 3.
    picocli.spring
    Provides classes and interfaces for integrating picocli with Spring Boot.
    picocli.spring.boot.autoconfigure
    Provides classes and interfaces for picocli Spring Boot Auto-configuration.
